        ,
        .
        .
        .
        ,
        n
        }
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle W_{n}(\Lambda ):=\{((a_{i})_{i=0,..n}\in A^{n}:\ \exists \mathbf {x} \in \Lambda \ s.t.\ x_{i}=a_{i}\ \forall i=0,...,n\}.}
  

In the same way, for the particular case of 
  
    
      
        
